        "description": "Retrospective observational study drawing on de-identified clinical registry data from three VAD implant centres. Operating conditions were not experimentally manipulated; patients were treated per standard of care and data were collected prospectively for registry purposes. Propensity-score matching was used to reduce confounding.",
