    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the full 13-factor evaluation and the supporting validation evidence. The observational registry study was characterised in the narrative as providing controlled-experiment-equivalent evidence owing to the tightly bounded operating envelope and rigorous propensity-score adjustment. On this basis the team concluded that the hemolysis validation requirement had been met and accepted the submission. The structured requiredVerificationMethod field specifying 'controlled-experiment' was not cross-checked against the activityType field of 'observational-study' recorded for the supporting activity, leaving the W-AR-03 inference gap undetected.",
